 \sum^{m}_{k = n} \frac{1}{k!} \leq \sum^{m}_{k = n} \frac{1}{n! n^{k-n}} \leq \sum^{m}_{k = n} \frac{1}{n! 2^{k-n}} \leq \frac{2}{n!}. 
